# OZOBATH E-Commerce Platform — Expert Architecture Plan

## 1. Executive Summary

OZOBATH is a premium e-commerce platform for **shower enclosures & bathroom fittings**, targeting homeowners, interior designers, architects, B2B dealers, and builders. The platform features a **fully dynamic content management system** — every element from banners to text to images is admin-controlled.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Fully Dynamic Architecture**: Every piece of content on every page (banners, images, text, product sections, testimonials, FAQ, blog highlights) is stored in the database and editable from the admin panel. No content is hardcoded.

---

## 2. Technology Decisions

### Database: **MongoDB Atlas (Free Tier → M10)**

| Factor | MongoDB | PostgreSQL |
|--------|---------|------------|
| Schema flexibility | ✅ Dynamic content needs flexible schemas | ❌ Rigid schemas |
| Product variations | ✅ Embedded arrays/objects natively | ⚠️ Requires JSON columns |
| CMS-style content | ✅ Perfect for dynamic page blocks | ❌ Needs complex joins |
| Free tier | ✅ 512MB free on Atlas | ❌ Requires paid hosting |
| Full-text search | ✅ Atlas Search built-in | ✅ Good with extensions |

**Verdict**: MongoDB is ideal for this e-commerce + CMS hybrid. Dynamic page sections, product variants, and flexible schemas align perfectly.

### Image/File Storage: **Cloudinary (Free Tier)**

| Feature | Cloudinary | AWS S3 | Firebase Storage |
|---------|-----------|--------|-----------------|
| Free quota | ✅ 25GB + 25K transforms/mo | ⚠️ 5GB (12mo only) | ✅ 5GB |
| Auto optimization | ✅ WebP, resize, crop built-in | ❌ Manual | ❌ Manual |
| CDN built-in | ✅ Global CDN | ❌ Needs CloudFront | ✅ |
| Video support | ✅ Video transforms | ✅ Storage only | ✅ Storage only |
| Cost at scale | Affordable | Cheapest at scale | Moderate |

**Verdict**: Cloudinary — auto image optimization, CDN, free tier, and transformations built-in. Perfect for product images and dynamic banners.

### Full Stack

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| **Client** | React 18 + Vite + TailwindCSS | Fast, component-driven, large ecosystem |
| **Admin** | Vue 3 + Vite + TailwindCSS | Separate SPA, cleaner admin UX, Vue's reactivity ideal for forms |
| **Backend** | Node.js + Express.js | JavaScript full-stack, async I/O, huge npm ecosystem |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas + Mongoose | Flexible schemas, free tier, great for CMS |
| **File Storage** | Cloudinary | Auto-optimized images, CDN, free tier |
| **Auth** | JWT + bcrypt + refresh tokens | Stateless, scalable |
| **Payment** | Razorpay | All Indian payment methods (UPI, cards, wallets, netbanking) |
| **Email** | Nodemailer + Gmail/SendGrid | OTP, order confirmations, notifications |
| **Real-time** | Socket.io | Video call notifications, live chat |
| **AI Chatbot** | Google Gemini API (free tier) | FAQ auto-response, product recommendations |

