## 4. Database Schema Design (MongoDB Collections)

### 4.1 Core Collections

#### `users`
```js
{
  name, email, phone, password (hashed),
  role: "customer" | "admin" | "superadmin",
  avatar, addresses: [{ label, line1, line2, city, state, zip, isDefault }],
  isActive, emailVerified, createdBy (for admin accounts),
  createdAt, updatedAt
}
```

#### `products`
```js
{
  name, slug, description, shortDescription,
  sku, price, compareAtPrice, costPrice,
  category (ref), subCategory,
  images: [{ url, publicId, alt, order }],
  variants: [{ name, options: [{ label, value, priceModifier }] }],
  specifications: [{ key, value }],
  badges: ["best-seller", "new", "featured"],
  stock, lowStockThreshold, isActive,
  seoTitle, seoDescription, seoKeywords,
  avgRating, reviewCount,
  createdAt, updatedAt
}
```

#### `categories`
```js
{
  name, slug, description,
  image: { url, publicId },
  parent (self-ref), order, isActive,
  seoTitle, seoDescription
}
```

#### `orders`
```js
{
  orderNumber (auto), user (ref),
  items: [{ product, name, image, price, quantity, variant }],
  shippingAddress, billingAddress,
  subtotal, shippingCost, discount, tax, total,
  coupon (ref), paymentMethod, paymentStatus,
  razorpayOrderId, razorpayPaymentId,
  status: "pending"|"confirmed"|"processing"|"shipped"|"delivered"|"cancelled"|"returned",
  trackingNumber, trackingUrl,
  notes, statusHistory: [{ status, date, note }],
  createdAt, updatedAt
}
```

### 4.2 Dynamic Content Collections

#### `dynamic_contents` — ★ The Heart of the CMS
```js
{
  page: "home" | "about" | "contact" | ...,
  section: "hero_banner" | "category_tiles" | "trust_badges" | ...,
  order: Number,
  isActive: Boolean,
  content: {
    title, subtitle, description,    // Text content
    buttonText, buttonLink,          // CTA
    image: { url, publicId, alt },   // Media
    video: { url, type },
    items: [{ ... }],                // For repeatable items
    backgroundColor, textColor,      // Styling
    customCSS
  },
  createdAt, updatedAt
}
```

#### `banners`
```js
{
  title, subtitle, description,
  image: { url, publicId, alt },
  mobileImage: { url, publicId },
  link, buttonText,
  page: "home" | "shop" | ...,
  position: "hero" | "promo" | "category",
  order, isActive, startDate, endDate
}
```

#### Other collections: `testimonials`, `faqs`, `blogs`, `reviews`, `coupons`, `experience_centres`, `b2b_enquiries`, `service_requests`, `video_call_slots`, `site_visit_bookings`, `newsletters`, `partners`, `carts`, `wishlists`, `seo_meta`, `admin_activity_logs`

