## 5. Authentication & Authorization

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Super Admin] -->|Creates| B[Admin]
    B -->|Manages| C[Products/Orders/Content]
    D[Customer] -->|Registers| E[Self-Signup]
    D -->|Actions| F[Shop/Cart/Orders/Reviews]
```

| Role | Permissions |
|------|------------|
| **Super Admin** | Everything + Create/manage admin accounts |
| **Admin** | Product/Order/Content/Blog/Coupon management |
| **Customer** | Browse, cart, order, review, wishlist, profile |

- **JWT Access Token** (15min) + **Refresh Token** (7 days) stored in httpOnly cookie
- Passwords hashed with bcrypt (12 rounds)
- Route guards with middleware: `auth()`, `roleGuard('admin', 'superadmin')`

---

## 6. Dynamic Content System — How It Works

> [!TIP]
> The key innovation is the **section-based content architecture**. Each page is composed of ordered sections, each independently editable from admin.

### Home Page Sections (all dynamic)
1. **Announcement Bar** — Promo text, link, background color
2. **Hero Banner Slider** — Multiple slides with image, title, subtitle, CTA
3. **Category Tiles** — Grid of categories with images, links
4. **Best Sellers** — Dynamically pulled from products with "best-seller" badge
5. **New Arrivals** — Latest products by date
6. **Trust Badges/USPs** — Icon + text pairs (Premium Quality, Warranty, etc.)
7. **Video Section** — YouTube/Vimeo embed URL + title + description
8. **Customer Testimonials** — Carousel of reviews with star ratings
9. **Google Reviews** — Embedded Google Place reviews
10. **Instagram Feed** — Instagram API or embed widget
11. **Blog Highlights** — Latest 3 blog posts
12. **Newsletter Signup** — Email form + success message
13. **Partner Logos** — "Trusted By" section with logo images
14. **FAQ Section** — Accordion Q&A

### Admin Content Editor Flow
```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Admin Opens Content Manager] --> B[Select Page]
    B --> C[View Sections for Page]
    C --> D[Edit Section Content]
    D --> E[Upload Images/Videos]
    E --> F[Preview Changes]
    F --> G[Publish / Save Draft]
    G --> H[Client Fetches Updated Content]
```

---

## 7. API Architecture

### Base URL: `/api/v1`

| Module | Endpoints | Auth |
|--------|----------|------|
| **Auth** | POST `/auth/register`, `/auth/login`, `/auth/refresh`, `/auth/forgot-password`, `/auth/reset-password` | Public |
| **Users** | GET/PUT `/users/me`, GET `/users` (admin) | Protected |
| **Products** | GET `/products`, GET `/products/:slug`, POST/PUT/DELETE (admin) | Mixed |
| **Categories** | GET `/categories`, POST/PUT/DELETE (admin) | Mixed |
| **Cart** | GET/POST/PUT/DELETE `/cart` | Customer |
| **Orders** | POST `/orders`, GET `/orders/my-orders`, PUT `/orders/:id/status` (admin) | Protected |
| **Wishlist** | GET/POST/DELETE `/wishlist` | Customer |
| **Reviews** | GET/POST `/reviews`, PUT `/reviews/:id/approve` (admin) | Mixed |
| **Coupons** | POST `/coupons/validate`, CRUD (admin) | Mixed |
| **Content** | GET `/content/:page`, POST/PUT/DELETE (admin) | Mixed |
| **Banners** | GET `/banners`, CRUD (admin) | Mixed |
| **Blog** | GET `/blogs`, GET `/blogs/:slug`, CRUD (admin) | Mixed |
| **FAQ** | GET `/faqs`, CRUD (admin) | Mixed |
| **Testimonials** | GET `/testimonials`, CRUD (admin) | Mixed |
| **Upload** | POST `/upload/image`, POST `/upload/images` | Admin |
| **Payment** | POST `/payment/create-order`, POST `/payment/verify` | Customer |
| **Booking** | POST `/bookings/video-call`, POST `/bookings/site-visit`, GET (admin) | Mixed |
| **Enquiry** | POST `/enquiries/b2b`, POST `/enquiries/service`, GET (admin) | Mixed |
| **Newsletter** | POST `/newsletter/subscribe` | Public |
| **Analytics** | GET `/analytics/dashboard` (admin) | Admin |
| **Admin Users** | CRUD `/admin/users` | SuperAdmin |

---

## 8. Payment Flow (Razorpay)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    Client->>Server: POST /payment/create-order {amount, orderId}
    Server->>Razorpay: razorpay.orders.create()
    Razorpay-->>Server: {razorpay_order_id}
    Server-->>Client: {orderId, razorpayOrderId, key}
    Client->>Razorpay: Open checkout modal
    Razorpay-->>Client: {payment_id, signature}
    Client->>Server: POST /payment/verify {payment_id, order_id, signature}
    Server->>Server: Verify HMAC signature
    Server->>Server: Update order status → "confirmed"
    Server-->>Client: {success, order}
```

---

## 9. Video Call Shopping (Shop Live)

| Component | Implementation |
|-----------|---------------|
| **Slot Management** | Admin creates available time slots in admin panel |
| **Booking** | Customer picks a slot, fills name/phone, books |
| **Notifications** | Email/SMS sent to customer + admin on booking |
| **Video Call** | Admin joins via Google Meet/Zoom link (auto-generated or manual) |
| **Status** | pending → confirmed → completed → cancelled |

---

## 10. AI Chatbot Architecture

- **Engine**: Google Gemini API (free tier: 15 RPM)
- **Knowledge Base**: FAQs, product info, policies loaded as context
- **Fallback**: If AI can't answer → "Connect with an agent" → WhatsApp redirect
- **Implementation**: Floating widget on all pages, stores conversation history

---

## 11. Key Design Principles

1. **Mobile-First**: TailwindCSS responsive design, 60%+ traffic will be mobile
2. **Performance**: Lazy loading images, code splitting, Cloudinary auto-optimization
3. **SEO**: Server-rendered meta tags, structured data (JSON-LD), sitemap
4. **Security**: Helmet.js, CORS, rate limiting, input sanitization, CSRF protection
5. **Scalability**: Stateless backend, MongoDB indexing, CDN for assets

---

## 12. Deployment Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Production (Hostinger VPS)"
        A[Nginx Reverse Proxy] --> B[Client :3000]
        A --> C[Admin :3001]
        A --> D[Server :5000]
        D --> E[MongoDB Atlas]
        D --> F[Cloudinary CDN]
        D --> G[Razorpay API]
    end
```

| Component | Deployment |
|-----------|-----------|
| **Client (React)** | Vite build → Nginx serve static |
| **Admin (Vue)** | Vite build → Nginx serve static |
| **Server (Express)** | PM2 process manager |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas (cloud) |
| **Files** | Cloudinary (cloud CDN) |
| **SSL** | Let's Encrypt (free) |
| **Domain** | ozobath.co.in |

