## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm run test` — Run server-side unit tests (Jest for API endpoints, controllers)
- `npm run test:api` — API integration tests with supertest
- Check each Vite dev server starts without errors:
  - `cd apps/client && npm run dev`
  - `cd apps/admin && npm run dev`
  - `cd apps/server && npm run dev`

### Manual Verification
- Verify MongoDB connection on server startup
- Test all API routes via Postman/browser
- Verify admin can log in and see dashboard
- Verify client homepage renders with dynamic content from API
- Verify image upload to Cloudinary works
- Verify Razorpay checkout flow
- Browser testing for responsive design

